Hello,
 
I hope you are well.
This email is to inform you that we are closing the present ticket.
As we have not received a response from you since a while, we understand that you may have resolved the issue or are no longer experiencing it.
If you are still experiencing the problem or have any further questions, please reply to this email or create a new ticket, and we will be happy to assist you.
 
Thank you for your understanding,
Best regards,
Alin Anca

Technical Support Engineer

Hello,

Thank you for your time today.
Regarding the client upgrade log files, you should find something regarding this in C:WINDOWSTEMP locally.
You may also check the Event Viewer for anything related to the installation of the MSI file.
For the AD Sync topic, please follow the steps presented in the user manual, I will add it here below:
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EndpointProtector_5.9.4/page/Content/EndpointProtector/Admin/DirectoryServices/Overview.htm
Please let us know the result after that.

Have a nice weekend,
